Why Monitor Your Servers?
Server monitoring has a lot of benefits. The biggest benefit is avoiding reactive panics. You can get a head start on issues occurring in your servers or applications before your users are impacted.
Along with this benefit, vou can also use monitoring to figure out how to;

Increase uptime
Improve hardware and software nerformance
Plan for the future by making the best use of your rsources

Implementing monitoring can give you an almost immediate return on investment, you can observe trends, spikes and anomalies that may indicate a problem
and then you can drill down to discover the root cause of the issue.


